form.text: The financial results of the group have, from the beginning of the 2000 financial year, been prepared in accordance with International Financial Reporting Standards.
Figures prior to 2000 have not been restated to comply with International Financial Reporting Standards.
During 2003 the group changed its accounting policy to capitalise borrowing costs on qualifying assets and its accounting treatment in respect of turnover. Figures prior to 2001
